#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mul.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mul"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:1
#: of
msgid ""
"Get Multiplication of dataframe and other, element-wise (binary operator "
"`mul`). Equivalent to ``*``, but with support to substitute a fill_value "
"for missing data in one of the inputs. With reverse version, `rmul`. "
"Among flexible wrappers (`add`, `sub`, `mul`, `div`, `mod`, `pow`) to "
"arithmetic operators: `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`, `//`, `%`, `**`."
msgstr ""
"获取 dataframe 和 other 的逐元素乘法（二元运算符 `mul`）。等价于 ``*``，"
"但支持为其中一个输入中的缺失数据替换 fill_value。有反向版本 `rmul`。在"
"算术运算符 `+`、`-`、`*`、`/`、`//`、`%`、`**` 上的灵活包装函数包括：`add"
"`、`sub`、`mul`、`div`、`mod`、`pow`。"

