#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:7
#: of
msgid "Any single or multiple element data structure, or list-like object."
msgstr "任意单个或多个元素的数据结构，或类列表对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:9
#: of
msgid ""
"Whether to compare by the index (0 or 'index') or columns (1 or "
"'columns'). For Series input, axis to match Series index on."
msgstr ""
"按索引（0 或 'index'）或列（1 或 'columns'）进行比较。对于 Series 输入，"
"指定要匹配 Series 索引的轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:12
#: of
msgid ""
"Broadcast across a level, matching Index values on the passed MultiIndex "
"level."
msgstr "在传递的 MultiIndex 级别上广播，匹配该级别的 Index 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:15
#: of
msgid ""
"Fill existing missing (NaN) values, and any new element needed for "
"successful DataFrame alignment, with this value before computation. If "
"data in both corresponding DataFrame locations is missing the result will"
" be missing."
msgstr ""
"在计算之前，用此值填充现有的缺失值（NaN）以及成功对齐 DataFrame 所需的"
"任何新元素。如果两个 DataFrame 对应位置的数据都缺失，则结果也会是缺失的。"

